theorem cast_choose {a b : ℕ} (h : a ≤ b) :
    (b.choose a : K) = nat.factorial b / (nat.factorial a * nat.factorial (b - a)) :=
  by
  have : ∀ {n : ℕ}, (nat.factorial n : K) ≠ 0 := fun n => Nat.cast_ne_zero.2 (factorial_ne_zero _)
  rw [eq_div_iff_mul_eq (mul_ne_zero this this)]
  rw_mod_cast [← mul_assoc, choose_mul_factorial_mul_factorial h]
